my-big-project/
│
├── frontend/          ← React
├── backend/           ← Node.js
├── django-backend/    ← Django + DRF
├── go-api/            ← Go + Fiber/PostgreSQL
├── rust-api/          ← (optional Rust backend)
├── csharp-api/        ← ASP.NET Core
└── python-script/     ← Some automation or mini feature


✅ 1. To-Do App (CRUD)
Add tasks (POST)

View all tasks (GET)

Mark as complete (PUT/PATCH)

Delete task (DELETE)

✅ 2. User Authentication
Create login/signup form in React

Create /api/login and /api/register routes in backend

Add JWT for secure authentication

✅ 3. Upload Profile Image (Node + Multer)
Add file input in frontend

Create file upload endpoint using multer in backend

✅ 4. Django Integration
Create a new folder django-backend/

Practice API with Django Rest Framework (DRF)

Connect it to PostgreSQL